{"tid":460010,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★Good News!! 175 吉利汽車10月總銷量按月增長15%","createTime":"2017-11-06T09:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T03:39:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e34100dd2e04dda200ea987d33381cf155b52ba","tid":460010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"吉利汽車公布，10月總銷量逾12.5萬部創新高，按年增長30%，按月增長15%。期內出口量按年減少32%至758部，中國市場總銷量增長約31%至近12.44萬部。<br />\n<br />\n集團今年首10個月總銷量約95.22萬部，按年增長約72%，並達全年銷量目標110萬部的87%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363296-20171106.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363296-20171106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LGXF8pnRWKgDDRU%2FAc5FZxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=911a5db1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363296-20171106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6dddd31b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363296-20171106.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d701ec80145e96fbf676253d3ae041aa4e7a3445","tid":460010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:33:00.000Z","msg":"$50 soon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88000c9d7abc9e732df1e889324ddbfd2d2779ce","tid":460010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/9-10-2017/Y4IqME.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-10-2017%2FY4IqME.gif&h=51c83c8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a37ce1c648e71276d941f4ac3bb13726cc3716e","tid":460010,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc